headline: Can Bad Bunny and Selena Gomez make Americans snack again?
summary: What does Bad Bunny, Selena Gomez and Walton Goggins all have in common? It might sound like a red carpet premiere, but major food companies are hoping that their star power attracts Americans’ appetite to snack again.
